summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS A 2014 HYUNDAI GENESIS. WHILE DRIVING AT VARIOUS SPEEDS THE VEHICLE HESITATED AND LOST MOTIVE POWER. THE SPEEDOMETER SHOWED A DECREASED SPEED. THE VEHICLE FAILED TO ACCELERATE ABOVE 20 MPH. THERE WERE NO WARNING LIGHTS ILLUMINATED. THE LOCAL DEALER AND MANUFACTURER WERE NOT CONTACTED. THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 60,000.
